{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the results of the N-gram model are compared with those presented in Alsudias and Rayson (2020), where TF-IDF-based frequency features and Word2Vecbased embedding features were employed.",
    "LR, RF, and SVM were selected as the classifiers.",
    "A detailed comparison of the proposed N-gram classifier against TF-IDF and Word2Vec is illustrated in Figs.",
    "6, 7, and 8 for the LR, RF, and SVM classifiers.",
    "Combining LR with N-grams leads to superior performance compared to LR using TF-IDF and Word2Vec alone."
  ]
}